      <p begin="01:35.860" end="01:39.580" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:35.860" end="01:35.960">A</span> <span begin="01:36.040" end="01:36.410">mint</span> <span begin="01:36.600" end="01:37.200">ju</span><span begin="01:37.200" end="01:37.420">lep,</span> <span begin="01:38.120" end="01:38.180">a</span> <span begin="01:38.300" end="01:38.680">mint</span> <span begin="01:38.850" end="01:39.430">ju</span><span begin="01:39.430" end="01:39.580">lep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一杯薄荷茱莉普，一杯薄荷茱莉普</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">ミント・ジュレップ ミント・ジュレップ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">민트 줄렙 민트 줄렙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un mint julep un mint julep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un julepe de menta, un julepe de menta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Mint Julep, ein Mint Julep</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um mint julep, um mint julep</span></p>
      <p begin="01:39.820" end="01:47.150" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:39.820" end="01:40.460">One</span> <span begin="01:40.610" end="01:41.080">mint</span> <span begin="01:41.160" end="01:41.760">ju</span><span begin="01:41.760" end="01:42.010">le</span><span begin="01:42.100" end="01:42.180">p</span> <span begin="01:42.660" end="01:43.170">wa</span><span begin="01:43.170" end="01:43.240">s</span> <span begin="01:43.240" end="01:43.340">the</span> <span begin="01:43.390" end="01:43.780">cau</span><span begin="01:43.780" end="01:43.820">se</span> <span begin="01:43.820" end="01:43.960">of</span> <span begin="01:44.000" end="01:44.350">it</span> <span begin="01:44.380" end="01:47.150">all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">一杯薄荷茱莉普就是这一切的起因</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">一杯のミント・ジュレップが 全ての発端だった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">민트 줄렙 한 잔이 이 모든 일의 원인이었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un mint julep a été la cause de tout ça</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un julepe de menta fue la causa de todo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Mint Julep war die Ursache für alles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Um mint julep foi a causa de tudo</span></p>
      <p begin="01:48.260" end="01:52.920" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:48.260" end="01:48.760">I</span> <span begin="01:49.070" end="01:49.610">don't</span> <span begin="01:49.670" end="01:50.000">want</span> <span begin="01:50.060" end="01:50.150">to</span> <span begin="01:50.210" end="01:50.790">bore</span> <span begin="01:50.790" end="01:51.160">you</span> <span begin="01:51.660" end="01:52.010">wi</span><span begin="01:52.010" end="01:52.110">th</span> <span begin="01:52.200" end="01:52.350">my</span> <span begin="01:52.400" end="01:52.730">trou</span><span begin="01:52.770" end="01:52.880">ble</span><span begin="01:52.880" end="01:52.920">s</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我不想拿我的烦心事来惹你心烦</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">俺の苦労話で 退屈させたくはないが</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내 고민으로 널 지루하게 하고 싶진 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne veux pas t'ennuyer avec mes problèmes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No quiero aburrirte con mis problemas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich will dich nicht mit meinen Problemen langweilen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não quero te entediar com meus problemas</span></p>
      <p begin="01:52.950" end="01:57.210" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:52.950" end="01:53.220">But</span> <span begin="01:53.300" end="01:53.500">from</span> <span begin="01:53.500" end="01:54.070">now</span> <span begin="01:54.070" end="01:54.600">on,</span> <span begin="01:54.630" end="01:55.120">I'll</span> <span begin="01:55.170" end="01:55.520">be</span> <span begin="01:56.000" end="01:56.440">thin</span><span begin="01:56.500" end="01:56.660">kin'</span> <span begin="01:56.710" end="01:57.050">dou</span><span begin="01:57.110" end="01:57.210">ble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但从今往后，我遇事定会三思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">これからは 慎重に行動しようと思う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하지만 이제부터는 신중하게 생각할 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mais à partir de maintenant je penserai pour deux</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pero de ahora en adelante, pensaré el doble</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Aber von nun an, werde ich doppelt denken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mas de agora em diante, vou pensar em dobro</span></p>
      <p begin="01:57.250" end="02:01.970" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:57.250" end="01:57.700">I'm</span> <span begin="01:57.790" end="01:58.380">through</span> <span begin="01:58.380" end="01:58.830">wi</span><span begin="01:58.830" end="01:58.910">th</span> <span begin="01:58.910" end="01:59.220">flir</span><span begin="01:59.220" end="01:59.370">tin'</span> <span begin="01:59.470" end="01:59.850">and</span> <span begin="02:00.370" end="02:00.720">drin</span><span begin="02:00.860" end="02:01.020">kin'</span> <span begin="02:01.070" end="02:01.370">whi</span><span begin="02:01.430" end="02:01.550">s</span><span begin="02:01.610" end="02:01.970">key</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我戒了风流，也戒了威士忌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">火遊びも ウイスキーももうたくさんだ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">바람 피우는 것도 위스키 마시는 것도 끝이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'en ai fini de flirter et de boire du whisky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">He terminado con el coqueteo y de beber whisky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich bin fertig mit Flirten und Whiskey trinken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Acabei com a paquera e de beber uísque</span></p>
      <p begin="02:01.420" end="02:06.560" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:01.420" end="02:01.560">I</span> <span begin="02:01.610" end="02:01.930">got</span> <span begin="02:02.090" end="02:02.490">si</span><span begin="02:02.490" end="02:02.580">x</span> <span begin="02:02.710" end="02:03.050">ex</span><span begin="02:03.050" end="02:03.160">tra</span> <span begin="02:03.210" end="02:03.580">chil</span><span begin="02:03.640" end="02:03.990">dren</span> <span begin="02:04.110" end="02:04.700">fro</span><span begin="02:04.700" end="02:04.750">m</span> <span begin="02:04.750" end="02:04.840">a-</span><span begin="02:04.900" end="02:05.220">get</span><span begin="02:05.260" end="02:05.380">tin'</span> <span begin="02:05.410" end="02:05.830">fri</span><span begin="02:05.830" end="02:05.920">s</span><span begin="02:05.980" end="02:06.560">ky</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就因为一时轻狂我多出了六个娃</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ja">羽目を外したせいで 6人も子供ができちまった</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">까불다가 아이가 여섯 명이나 더 생겨버렸으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'ai eu six enfants en plus pour avoir été trop joueur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tengo seis hijos extra por ponerme juguetón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich habe sechs zusätzliche Kinder vom Übermütigwerden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ganhei seis filhos extras por ficar assanhado</span></p>
